These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-1::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, journalist
1. the accountant is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |
| Job   | journalist | accountant |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-2::.
There 2 different types of food: radish, pepper
1. the person eating pepper is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |
| Food   | radish | pepper |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-3::.
